title: SWAT incident blocks Lake Shore Drive downtown

SWAT incident blocks Lake Shore Drive downtown Downtown SWAT incident Armando L. Sanchez / Chicago Tribune 
Two armored vehicles are on either side of a car containing a man on Queen's Landing just off Lake Shore Drive, east of Buckingham Fountain, Feb. 12, 2017.
